c: 2
v: 171
t: "Yeh log jinhon ne khuda ke bataye huey tareeqe par chalne se inkar kardiya hai inki haalat bilkul aisi hai jaise charwaha jaanwaron ko pukarta hai aur woh haank pukaar ki sada ke siwa kuch nahin suntey. Yeh behre hain , gungay hain andhey hain, isliye koi baat inki samajh mein nahin aati"